title: Jonathan Coulton - Discography
description:
This is all of Jonathan Coulton's music to date.

Jonathan Coulton is an American folk rock singer-songwriter, famous for his songs containing themes of geek culture as well as his rise to popularity through the use of the internet.

This pack includes -

- Smoking Monkey
- Thing A Week (all... 1-4)
- Our Bodies, Ourselves, Our Cybernetic Arms
- The Aftermath
- Other Experiments
- Where Tradition Meets Tomorrow
- Songs From Ze Frank's "The Show"

All mp3, and not in RAR, so that if you already have some you can pick and choose as to what you want.

Enjoy. This guy is absolutely amazing =]
